text: Ede Mađar (28 July 1931 - 13 April 2005) was a Serbian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Serbian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Subotica
